body:
Using `1.47.2` and Nx, it is still really flaky.

The playwright does not seem to be able to properly start the dev-server.
And the UI starts, but no tests are loaded
```
Error: Process from config.webServer was not able to start. Exit code: 1
```

Disabling the webserver and starting the application manually, makes it that we can test again.
```
 // webServer: {
  //   command: 'npx nx serve expo',
  //   url: 'http://localhost:4200',
  //   reuseExistingServer: true,
  //   cwd: workspaceRoot,
  // },
```

(don't know if it is related, or if it should be a new issue)

